Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:23.62,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,心中滿溢情誼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:27.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,足尖輕柔躍動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:30.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,世界如虹綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:35.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,將那小小希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:39.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,種子緊握手中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:43.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,懷揣堅信馳騁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.17,0:01:53.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,悲喜皆是色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:57.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,繪就璀璨未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:00.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無數次的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:05.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,促我跨步前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:09.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,輕笑說出無礙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,只因有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:14.14,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無論何時何地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:17.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,積極樂觀不變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:20.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我願伸手相牽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.22,0:02:22.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,若可為你緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,攜手共赴天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,遍歷閃耀世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:30.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,定有未知景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:37.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,在那遠方等待
