Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:30.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不安なんておやつにして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,回り道だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:35.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,たどり着けば正解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:39.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,考えるよりも先に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,心は動いちゃうから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.45,0:22:47.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,予定調和なんてありえないんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:51.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,セメント色したビルも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:55.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,不機嫌すぎる空でも全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:23:00.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君が笑えば思い出になる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:04.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,心の容量いっぱいに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:07.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,保存した思いを力に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,理想と違う現実に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:13.71,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,足がすくんじゃうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:17.26,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,心の中にあるコンパスは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:20.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,知っている　指し示している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.95,0:23:23.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,何が待っているかは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:26.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,進む未知の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:29.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,進む道の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:31.93,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どこまでも行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:31.93,EDJP_S,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1798,10)}ゆ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:32.65,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:13.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,千里之行　始於足下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:19.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,天涯海角　皆是通途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:20.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:27.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,若不放棄便有無盡可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:30.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,將不安當作開胃的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:32.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,即便百轉千回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:35.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,抵達終點便是正途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:39.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,思考尚未開始反應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳已經怦然加速
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.45,0:22:47.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,預定？配合？根本無從談起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.27,0:22:51.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無論水泥色的單調大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:55.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,還是惹人不快天空等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.79,0:23:00.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有你笑容便是珍貴回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:04.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,留存心間時時滿溢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:07.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,思念化作無盡動力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,理想現實落差懸殊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:13.71,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,令人不禁停步駐足
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:17.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,心中的那枚指南針
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:20.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,從不迷惘直指前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.95,0:23:23.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,且問有何相待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:26.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,盡在未知前方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:29.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,盡在通途彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:31.93,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,天涯海角　攜手共赴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:32.65,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,出發吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//zheng
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本打算開好會就吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我道歉了啊　再買就是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是京都限定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在上哪買去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.43,0:00:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼稀罕的話怎麼都不寫個名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菊石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來杏花碳是那支遊擊隊的倖存者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要親手消滅那隻菊石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我畏懼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.39,0:00:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會幫你報仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安心睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由衣碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什麼　快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你想一個人攔下它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有別的辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Attack Function
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,座標瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.52,0:01:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去博多的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對手實在太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千萬打中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由衣　你拉開距離了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有回應　無法確認
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果她用的是Attack Function的默認輸出…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老朽加了限制器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量和生命值都不會清零的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制器的餘量還是不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野碳　快呼叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大前鋒　收到請回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標表面有8%受損
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干擾波已消失
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮彈飛行時間剩餘160秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大前鋒　請立即撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由衣　快回答　由衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,限制器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有你的御宅老
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再給我等會兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡　還這麼鬧騰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠距制導炮彈飛行時間剩餘140秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大前鋒請立即撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會產生衝擊波的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一發就當是威懾了　快點離開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下它要是再動那不又一樣了嗎
