Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}行啊　還啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美春　看到我加的麵了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道　沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加的麵哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}別把手指往喉嚨裡捅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:21:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多行了吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}誰讓你把我的麵給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃下去的東西誰會還啊　腦子有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我加的麵到底去哪了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵加五份
